l\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 15, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jmr1702546522512.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jmr1702546522512.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jmr1702546522512.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jmr1702546522512\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Script Editor enables you to write ProcScript and JavaScript that controls the\n\t\tbehavior of the component.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface also allows you to configure the Script Editor settings.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzq1702624284885.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Configure Indentation in the Script Editor</a><p>By default, the Script Editor is configured to indent code using a tab character that is equivalent to 4 spaces. If your coding standards or preferences call for the use of spaces or a different tab size, you can change this configuration.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mmv1702546628362.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Enabling bi-directional writing for an RTL language</a><p>Right-to-left (RTL) languages are written from right to left of the screen, such as Arabic, Hebrew, and Persian languages. English is a Left-to-right (LTR) language. Bi-directional writing supports both RTL and LTR languages simultaneously. By default, bi-directional writing is disabled in Uniface IDE editor. To enable bi-directional writing for an RTL language, you need to update the usys.ini file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epb1702547154823.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Configuring the auto-indentation feature</a><p>Auto-indent is an automated feature in the Uniface Script Editor that automatically adjusts the indentation of Proc lines, ensuring consistent and readable formatting. This feature is enabled by default and can be disabled by setting autoindent=off in the usys.ini file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5564139\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5564139\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configure the Script Editor Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 15, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Script Editor enables you to write ProcScript and JavaScript that controls the behavior of the component. Uniface also allows you to configure the Script Editor settings. Related Links Configure Indentation in the Script Editor By default, the Script Editor is configured to indent code using a tab character that is equivalent to 4 spaces. If your coding standards or preferences call for the use of spaces or a different tab size, you can change this configuration. Enabling bi-directional writing for an RTL language Right-to-left (RTL) languages are written from right to left of the screen, such as Arabic, Hebrew, and Persian languages. English is a Left-to-right (LTR) language. Bi-directional writing supports both RTL and LTR languages simultaneously. By default, bi-directional writing is disabled in Uniface IDE editor. To enable bi-directional writing for an RTL language, you need to update the usys.ini file. Configuring the auto-indentation feature Auto-indent is an automated feature in the Uniface Script Editor that automatically adjusts the indentation of Proc lines, ensuring consistent and readable formatting. This feature is enabled by default and can be disabled by setting autoindent=off in the usys.ini file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}